snippet.title: WARMACHINE: Tactics Kickstarter - Privateer Press Interactive
snippet.description:
Support our Kickstarter project at: http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/409030043/warmachine-tactics

Turn-based tactical combat for PC and Mac, set in the steam-powered world of the award-winning WARMACHINE tabletop game.

Bring WARMACHINE from the tabletop to your desktop!

• Squad-level, turn based tactics!
• Single-player campaign with an extensive, story-driven experience!
• Online multiplayer with synchronous and asynchronous support!
• Incredible exclusive rewards for backing the project!

http://www.warmachinetactics.com
